data.title: Famous Personality of Himachal Pradesh
data.meta_description: Famous-Personality-of-Himachal-Pradesh - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides brief biographies of famous personalities from Himachal Pradesh, including freedom fighters, artists, writers, and politicians. Some of the personalities profiled include Anand Chand, the first chief commissioner of Bilaspur state; Anant Ram, a great patriot and freedom fighter; and Baba Kanshi Ram, who was given the title of "Pahari Gandhi" for his work. The document also mentions personalities from various fields like Bakshi Pratap Singh and Narain Chand Prashar, who were renowned painters that depicted the Himalayas.
